# Playtest output from `openttd-playtest` (the savegame, logs, and a throwaway
# OpenTTD home). It's regenerated on every run — keep it out of the workspace diff.
openttd-out/

# Last-working-bot checkpoint that `openttd-playtest` snapshots so the scorer can
